Branchometer - a 2D leaf morphometry program
--------------------------------------------

Code                             Pirom Konglerd 2012-2014
								 pirom.konglerd@gmail.com

Git repo and linux compilation   Fredrik Jansson
                                 fjansson@abo.fi				


Compiling and dependencies
--------------------------------
The program requires Qt4.

#install qmake qt4 and glut, on Debian, Ubuntu and relatives
sudo aptitude install qt4-qmake qt4-dev-tools freeglut3-dev

# get the source code with git
git clone https://github.com/UvA-compsci/branchometer.git

#create the make file, on Linux
qmake -o Makefile branchometer.linux.pro

#create the make file, on OSX
qmake -o Makefile branchometer.osx.pro

#compile with make
make


